 (a) together with a brief review of actual performance with ﾂｷ reference to those targets; ( c) an administrative report on the activities of the Authority during the previous year and the current year and an account of the activities which are likely to b‾ taken up during the next financial year; ﾂｷ . ‾ -- 6 of 10 -- 124 THE GAZETTE Qf.JNDIA: EXTRAORDINARY [PART ll=-Sec. 3(i)] ----------- ,...__.___.... ‾---ﾂｷ (d) important changes in the organizational set up of the Authority; (e) report on employer-employees relations and welfare activities of the Authority; arid ' . (f) report on such other miscellaneous matters as deemed fit by the Authority for repo‾ting to the Central Government. ﾂｷ(3) The annual report shall, after adoption at a meeting of the Authority, be signed by the .Chairperson and authenticated by affixing the common seal of the Authority and the reiuisite number of copies thereof shall beﾂｷ submitted to the Central Government by the 30t. day of September in ea.ch calendar year. ANNEXURE-I RET_URNS AND STATE.MENTS AND OTHER PARTICULARS REQUIRED TO BE FURNISHED QUARTERLY BY WAREHOUSING DEVELOPMENT AND REGULATORY AUTHORITY (See rule 3) I. ﾂｷ .Statement of registration of warehouses by Authority. SI. . Number of Number of warehouses Number of warehouses No. applications received registered during the quarter .. pending for registration for registration with details II. Statement of the periodical inspection of warehouses conducted by the Authority/or its authorized representative to monitor the quality .of service provided by the warehouses. ﾂｷ i SI. Warehouse Inspection conducted Observation of Authority Remedial steps ﾂｷNo. during the quarter with details taken . ' III. Statement of registration of accreditation agencies by Authority. SL Number of application No. of accreditation agencies Number of applications of No. ﾂｷ received from registered during 窶｢the quarter accreditation agencies accreditation agencies . with details pending for registration 